%mathpiper,defelanor"

/*
Note:tk:since this version of NormalForm is only used in univariate functions, and since
 the standard version of NormalForm is published as a def in standard.mrw,
I am not publishing it as a def here.
*/

0 # NormalForm(UniVariate(_var,_first,_coefs)) <--
    ExpandUniVariate(var,first,coefs);

%/mathpiper